                                    oc:tableCaption "### Freshness" ;
                                    oc:tableMarkdown """| Recency | Confidence impact |
|---------|------------------|
| Today / yesterday | High confidence for current state |
| This week | Good confidence |
| This month | Moderate — things may have changed |
